WEBVTT

00:01.335 --> 00:02.370
- Previously on Haven...

00:02.503 --> 00:03.868
- FBI! Who are you?
- Haven PD.

00:04.004 --> 00:05.869
Keep your hands
where I can see them.

00:06.006 --> 00:07.041
- What am I gonna do,
pull out another gun?

00:07.174 --> 00:09.210
People do things in Haven.
- What things?

00:09.343 --> 00:12.255
- A woman whose moods
affected the weather.

00:12.387 --> 00:14.594
Another man's shadow
kills people.

00:14.723 --> 00:18.261
- Haven is chock-full
of the ungodly!

00:18.393 --> 00:20.133
- How do you die?
- Some guy with a tattoo

00:20.270 --> 00:21.601
of a maze
with four little people

00:21.730 --> 00:23.311
at each of the compass points.

00:23.440 --> 00:24.395
- I couldn't feel anything.

00:24.525 --> 00:26.390
I thought I was sick.

00:26.527 --> 00:27.983
Audrey, I can feel
her touch.

00:28.111 --> 00:29.897
- There's gonna come a day
when you're gonna wish

00:30.030 --> 00:31.645
you'd just taken the chance
just to make nice

00:31.782 --> 00:33.067
with your old man.

00:33.200 --> 00:34.690
- You want me to let
bygones be bygones?

00:34.826 --> 00:36.157
- We're never gonna get along,
are we?

00:36.286 --> 00:37.321
- So the crack on the boat?

00:37.454 --> 00:38.739
- We need to get this place
under control.

00:38.872 --> 00:40.408
- You haven't changed, Lucy.

00:40.541 --> 00:41.576
- Lucy was my mother.

00:41.708 --> 00:42.743
- When I had my seizure,

00:42.876 --> 00:43.911
I shattered a glass.

00:44.044 --> 00:46.251
It cut her
deep on the sole of her foot.

